msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.251"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an3.100:8.1"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco aḍḍhakahāpaṇenapi bandhanaṃ nigacchati, kahāpaṇenapi "
"bandhanaṃ nigacchati, kahāpaṇasatenapi bandhanaṃ nigacchati."
msgstr ""
"Take the case of a person who is thrown in jail for stealing half a dollar, "
"a dollar, or a hundred dollars."

msgctxt "an3.100:8.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco aḍḍhakahāpaṇenapi na bandhanaṃ nigacchati, "
"kahāpaṇenapi na bandhanaṃ nigacchati, kahāpaṇasatenapi na bandhanaṃ "
"nigacchati."
msgstr ""
"While another person who isn’t thrown in jail for stealing half a dollar, a "
"dollar, or a hundred dollars."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an3.100:9.1"
msgid ""
"Kathaṃrūpo, bhikkhave, aḍḍhakahāpaṇenapi bandhanaṃ nigacchati, kahāpaṇenapi "
"bandhanaṃ nigacchati, kahāpaṇasatenapi bandhanaṃ nigacchati?"
msgstr ""
"What kind of person is thrown in jail for stealing half a dollar, a dollar, "
"or a hundred dollars?"

msgctxt "an3.100:9.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco daliddo hoti appassako appabhogo."
msgstr "A person who is poor, with few possessions and little wealth."

msgctxt "an3.100:9.3"
msgid ""
"Evarūpo, bhikkhave, aḍḍhakahāpaṇenapi bandhanaṃ nigacchati, kahāpaṇenapi "
"bandhanaṃ nigacchati, kahāpaṇasatenapi bandhanaṃ nigacchati."
msgstr ""
"That kind of person is thrown in jail for stealing half a dollar, a dollar, "
"or a hundred dollars."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an3.100:10.1"
msgid ""
"Kathaṃrūpo, bhikkhave, aḍḍhakahāpaṇenapi na bandhanaṃ nigacchati, "
"kahāpaṇenapi na bandhanaṃ nigacchati, kahāpaṇasatenapi na bandhanaṃ "
"nigacchati?"
msgstr ""
"What kind of person isn’t thrown in jail for stealing half a dollar, a "
"dollar, or a hundred dollars?"

msgctxt "an3.100:10.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco aḍḍho hoti mahaddhano mahābhogo."
msgstr "A person who is rich, affluent, and wealthy."

# This sutta has a breathtakingly cynical view of the justice system…
msgctxt "an3.100:10.3"
msgid ""
"Evarūpo, bhikkhave, aḍḍhakahāpaṇenapi na bandhanaṃ nigacchati, kahāpaṇenapi "
"na bandhanaṃ nigacchati, kahāpaṇasatenapi na bandhanaṃ nigacchati."
msgstr ""
"That kind of person isn’t thrown in jail for stealing half a dollar, a "
"dollar, or a hundred dollars."

msgctxt "an3.100:10.4"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, idhekaccassa puggalassa appamattakaṃ pāpakammaṃ "
"kataṃ."
msgstr ""
"This is how it is in the case of a person who does a trivial bad deed, but "
"they go to hell."

msgctxt "an3.100:10.5"
msgid "Tamenaṃ nirayaṃ upaneti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.100:10.6"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekaccassa puggalassa tādisaṃyeva appamattakaṃ pāpakammaṃ "
"kataṃ diṭṭhadhammavedanīyaṃ hoti, nāṇupi khāyati, kiṃ bahudeva."
msgstr ""
"While another person does the same trivial bad deed, but experiences it in "
"the present life, without even a bit left over, not to speak of a lot. …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "an3.100:11.1"
msgid ""
"Kathaṃrūpassa, bhikkhave, puggalassa appamattakaṃ pāpakammaṃ kataṃ, tamenaṃ "
"nirayaṃ upaneti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.100:11.2"
msgid ""
